This has already been implemented.
If you want the "quote prefix"; you need the latest develop branch from github, and this needs to be applied as a style because the content is still simply "name".

```php
$objPHPExcel->getActiveSheet()->setCellValue('A1', "name");
$objPHPExcel->getActiveSheet()->getStyle('A1')->setQuotePrefix(true);
```
